transcripts: Britax the leader in safety technology designed to b-safe 35 infant car seat to deliver a comfy safe and secure ride for your baby on the road ahead. Install with confidence using the one hand spring assisted recline and dual level indicators to make sure the infant car seats angle is correct. The safe center latch installation system uses the e.z. center pole straps that cinched down securely in a stowaway neatly within the base. With our exclusive safe cell impact protection and integrated system of safety components work together to protect your baby well beyond the federal safety standards. And safe cell complete side impact protection surrounds your baby in a deep protective shell shielding your child from crash forces and debris. The b-safe 35 features an adjustable four position harness and two position buckle to grow with your child. The e.z. release harness button makes it simple to loosen the harness straps and the extra large canopy protect your baby from the rain and sun. The click and go system featuring a quick release handle makes it easy to transfer the b-safe 35 to any Britax stroller. A simple click lets you know that your child's car seat is securely attached and the same quick release handle releases from the stroller back to the base from the leader in safety technology. The Britax b-safe 35 allows you to travel with confidence knowing your baby is comfy safe and secure on the road ahead.
